;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>เทรนด์ Eco Packaging ปี 2025–2026</h2><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>FAQ — ถุงบรรจุภัณฑ์ผ้าและ Eco Packaging OEM</h2><div style="margin-bottom:2rem;"><div style="border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:0.85rem;"><div style="background:#f8fafc;padding:0.9rem 1.25rem;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;color:#0f172a;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;flex-shrink:0;">Q</span>ถุงผ้า Cotton Canvas กันน้ำได้ไหม?</div><div style="padding:0.9rem 1.25rem;font-size:0.88rem;color:#475569;line-height:1.85;border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;">ถุง Cotton มาตรฐานไม่กันน้ำ แต่สามารถเคลือบ Wax หรือ PU Coating เพื่อเพิ่มคุณสมบัติกันน้ำได้ในระดับหนึ่ง</div></div><div style="border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:0.85rem;"><div style="background:#f8fafc;padding:0.9rem 1.25rem;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;color:#0f172a;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;flex-shrink:0;">Q</span>MOQ ถุงผ้า OEM เริ่มต้นที่เท่าไหร่?</div><div style="padding:0.9rem 1.25rem;font-size:0.88rem;color:#475569;line-height:1.85;border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;">ถุงผ้าสำเร็จรูปแบบ Stock MOQ เริ่มต้น 100–500 ชิ้น Custom Print เริ่ม 500–1,000 ชิ้น Embroidery เริ่ม 1,000 ชิ้น</div></div></div><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>สรุป</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">Eco Packaging ไม่ใช่แค่กระแส แต่คือทิศทางที่ตลาดกำลังมุ่งไปอย่างหลีกเลี่ยงไม่ได้ การเลือกถุงบรรจุภัณฑ์ผ้าและวัสดุ Eco ที่เหมาะสมตั้งแต่ต้น จะช่วยให้แบรนด์ OEM ของคุณก้าวไปพร้อมกับตลาดโลกได้อย่างยั่งยืน</p><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fffbeb,#fff7ed);border-radius:14px;padding:1.5rem 1.75rem;border-left:5px solid #F59E0B;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"><p style="margin:0;font-size:0.97rem;color:#1e293b;line-height:2;font-style:italic;">Eco Packaging ไม่ใช่แค่กระแส แต่คือทิศทางที่ตลาดกำลังมุ่งไปอย่างหลีกเลี่ยงไม่ได้ การเลือกถุงบรรจุภัณฑ์ผ้าและวัสดุ Eco ที่เหมาะสมตั้งแต่ต้น จะช่วยให้แบรนด์ OEM ของคุณก้าวไปพร้อมกับตลาดโลกได้อย่างยั่งยืน</p></div><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b 0%,#0f172a 100%);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem 1.75rem;text-align:center;margin-top:2.5rem;"><p style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin:0 0 0.4rem;">ดูถุงบรรจุภัณฑ์ผ้าและ Eco Packaging ทั้งหมด</p><a href="/categories" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:1rem;padding:0.65rem 2.25rem;background:#F59E0B;color:#fff;border-radius:999px;font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:800;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.03em;">ดูสินค้าทั้งหมด</a></div></div>', '<div style="font-family:\'Sarabun\',sans-serif;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;color:#374151;line-height:1.9;"><span style="display:inline-block;background:#FFF7ED;color:#F59E0B;border:1px solid #FDE68A;border-radius:999px;padding:0.2rem 0.75rem;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">OEM Guide</span><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>What Are Fabric Bags and Eco Packaging in OEM?</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">Popular fabric bag and eco packaging types in the OEM market:</p><ul style="list-style:none;margin:0 0 2rem;padding:0;"><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Linen Bags — naturally biodegradable</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Cotton Canvas Bags — durable and reusable</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Jute Bags — rustic aesthetic for Organic brand positioning</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Biodegradable Non-woven Bags — low cost, compostable</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Kraft Paper Boxes — highly popular eco alternative</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>PCR Foil Pouches (Post-Consumer Recycled) — for Premium Refill products</span></li></ul><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Why Eco Packaging Matters for OEM Businesses Today</h2><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Choosing the Right Fabric Bag for Your OEM Product</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">Not every eco packaging solution suits every product. Consider:</p><div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0.6rem;margin-bottom:2rem;"><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.55rem 0.75rem;background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:8px;"><span style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span><span style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">Product weight and dimensions</span></div><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.55rem 0.75rem;background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:8px;"><span style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span><span style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">Protection from moisture and UV light</span></div><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.55rem 0.75rem;background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:8px;"><span style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span><span style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">Compatibility with packing process (Hand Pack vs Automation)</span></div><div style="display:f