ustify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:0.05rem;">4</span><span style="font-size:0.92rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.75;">Confirm MOQ and production timeline</span></li><li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;padding:0.85rem 1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:10px;"><span style="background:#F59E0B;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:0.8rem;min-width:1.6rem;height:1.6rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:0.05rem;">5</span><span style="font-size:0.92rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.75;">Approve samples before full production</span></li><li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;padding:0.85rem 1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:10px;"><span style="background:#F59E0B;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:0.8rem;min-width:1.6rem;height:1.6rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:0.05rem;">6</span><span style="font-size:0.92rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.75;">Full production run and QC inspection</span></li></ul><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>FAQ — OEM Spout Packaging</h2><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Conclusion</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">Choosing the right spout enhances user experience a