-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Shampoos and conditioners</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Hand sanitizer gels and liquid soaps</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Foundation and BB Cream</li>\n</ul>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Types of Pump Dispensers for OEM Production</h2>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Key Factors When Selecting an OEM Pump Dispenser</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">Choosing the wrong pump type can lead to leaks, clogging, or premature product degradation. Carefully consider:</p>\n\n<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Bottle neck finish (24mm, 28mm, etc.)</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Product viscosity and density</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Dosage volume per press (0.5–2ml)</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Pump head material (PP, Aluminum, ABS)</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Formula compatibility</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">GMP certification and safety standards</span></div>\n</div>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Why Airless Pump Is Trending in 2025</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">Skincare in 2025 is driven by Active Ingredients such as Retinol, Vitamin C, and Peptides — all of which degrade when exposed to air and light. Airless Pump systems are the optimal solution:</p>\n\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Decorating Pump Dispensers for Brand Identity</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">Pump dispensers offer multiple decoration options to build a distinctive OEM brand:</p>\n\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0 0 2rem; padding: 0;">\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Electroplating (Silver/Gold) for Luxury brand positioning</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Matte or Glossy spray coating to match brand tone</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Hot Stamp logo on pump head</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Full bottle + pump set screen printing</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Frosted/Transparent material for Clean Beauty aesthetics</li>\n</ul>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">FAQ — OEM Pump Dispensers</h2>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Conclusion</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">The right pump dispenser instantly elevates your OEM brand\'s perceived value. Especially Airless systems — the preferred choice for next-generation skincare with active ingredients.</p>\n\n<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b 0%,#0f172a 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem 1.75rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">\n<p style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 0.4rem;">Interested in OEM Pump Dispensers? Contact us for samples and a free quote.</p>\n<a style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.65rem 2.25rem; background: #F59E0B; color: #fff; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.03em;" href="/categories">Browse All Products</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
  (7171, 717, 'rich_text', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div style="font-family: \'Sarabun\',sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; color: #374151; line-height: 1.9;">\n\n<span style="display: inline-block; background: #FFF7ED; color: #f59e0b; border: 1px solid #FDE68A; border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">คู่มือ OEM</span>\n<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#fffbeb 0%,#fff7ed 100%); border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; padding: 1.35rem 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1rem; color: #1e293b; line-height: 1.95;">บรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่า OEM หมายถึงหลอดและแปรงมาสคาร่าที่ผลิตตามสเปคของแบรนด์ ไม่ว่าจะเป็นขนาด ทรง สี และรูปแบบแปรง ถือเป็นชิ้นส่วนที่สร้าง First Impression ให้กับแบรนด์ Cosmetics ได้ชัดเจนที่สุด</div>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">บรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่า OEM คืออะไร</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">บรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่า OEM ประกอบด้วยส่วนหลัก ได้แก่</p>\n\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0 0 2rem; padding: 0;">\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>หลอดมาสคาร่า (Tube) — วัสดุ PP, ABS หรือ Aluminum</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>ฝาพร้อมแปรง (Wand &amp; Brush) — ขนาด รูปทรง และวัสดุแปรงหลากหลาย</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Wiper Ring — ควบคุมปริมาณสูตรที่ติดแปรง</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>ฉลากและการตกแต่งภายนอก — Hot Stamp, Silk Screen, Sleeve</li>\n</ul>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">ประเภทของแปรงมาสคาร่าและผลลัพธ์ที่ได้</h2>\n<div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">\n<div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">\n<div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem; flex: 1; min-width: 0;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🪄</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.87rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.4;">Straight Brush</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.65;">แปรงตรงคลาสสิก ให้ความยาวและเวลามาสคาร่าทาง่าย</div>\n</div>\n<div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem; flex: 1; min-width: 0;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🌀</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.87rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.4;">Curved Brush</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.65;">แปรงโค้ง ช่วย Lift และม้วน Curl ขนตาได้ดีขึ้น</div>\n</div>\n<div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem; flex: 1; min-width: 0;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">💎</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.87rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.4;">Ball Tip Brush</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.65;">ปลายกลม ทาได้แม่นยำทั้งขนตาบนและล่าง</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">\n<div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem; flex: 1; min-width: 0;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🔥</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.87rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.4;">Spoolie / Comb</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.65;">หวีขนตา แยกเส้นขนตาและลด Clump ได้ดีเยี่ยม</div>\n</div>\n<div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem; flex: 1; min-width: 0;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">⚡</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.87rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.4;">Fibered Brush</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.65;">ขนแปรงหนาแน่น เพิ่ม Volume และ Thickness ให้ขนตา</div>\n</div>\n<div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem; flex: 1; min-width: 0;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✨</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.87rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.4;">Flexible Brush</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.65;">วัสดุแปรงยืดหยุ่น ลดการ Clump เหมาะกับสูตร Waterproof</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">วิธีเลือกหลอดมาสคาร่า OEM ให้ตรงกับ Positioning แบรนด์</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">บรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่าต้องสื่อสาร Positioning แบรนด์ได้ชัดเจนตั้งแต่แรกเห็น ควรพิจารณาดังนี้</p>\n\n<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">ทรงหลอด: ทรงกระบอก ทรงแบน หรือเรียวยาว</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">วัสดุหลอด: PP ต้นทุนต่ำ vs ABS พรีเมียม vs Aluminum Luxury</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">สีและ Finish: Black Matte, Glossy, Rose Gold, Holographic</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">ขนาดบรรจุ: 7ml–15ml ขึ้นอยู่กับช่องทางการขาย</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">ฉลาก: Sleeve Wrap, Heat Shrink หรือ Direct Print</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">ขนาดและรูปทรงแปรงตามผลลัพธ์ที่ต้องการ</span></div>\n</div>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">เทรนด์บรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่า OEM ปี 2025</h2>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">FAQ — บรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่า OEM</h2>\n<div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">\n<div style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 0.85rem;">\n<div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #0f172a; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">Q</span>MOQ ขั้นต่ำสำหรับหลอดมาสคาร่าคัสตอมคือเท่าไหร่?</div>\n<div style="padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #475569; line-height: 1.85; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">โดยทั่วไป MOQ เริ่มต้นที่ 3,000–5,000 ชิ้นสำหรับแม่พิมพ์ใหม่ หากใช้ Stock Mold สามารถลด MOQ ได้เหลือ 1,000 ชิ้น</div>\n</div>\n<div style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 0.85rem;">\n<div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #0f172a; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">Q</span>ทดสอบความเข้ากันได้ระหว่างสูตรมาสคาร่าและบรรจุภัณฑ์ได้อย่างไร?</div>\n<div style="padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #475569; line-height: 1.85; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">ต้องทำ Compatibility Test โดยบรรจุสูตรลงหลอดและทดสอบที่อุณหภูมิ 40–50°C เป็นเวลา 3 เดือน เพื่อตรวจสอบการเปลี่ยนแปลงทางเคมีและกายภาพ</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">สรุป</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">บรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่า OEM ที่ดีต้องสมดุลระหว่างฟังก์ชัน ความสวยงาม และความเข้ากันได้กับสูตร การเลือกแปรงและหลอดที่ใช่จะช่วยให้แบรนด์ใหม่สร้างความประทับใจได้ตั้งแต่ Shelf Presence</p>\n\n<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#fffbeb,#fff7ed); border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem; border-left: 5px solid #F59E0B; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">\n<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.97rem; color: #1e293b; line-height: 2; font-style: italic;">บรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่า OEM ที่ดีต้องสมดุลระหว่างฟังก์ชัน ความสวยงาม และความเข้ากันได้กับสูตร การเลือกแปรงและหลอดที่ใช่จะช่วยให้แบรนด์ใหม่สร้างความประทับใจได้ตั้งแต่ Shelf Presence</p>\n\n</div>\n<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b 0%,#0f172a 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem 1.75rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">\n<p style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 0.4rem;">สั่งผลิตบรรจุภัณฑ์มาสคาร่า OEM กับเราวันนี้</p>\n<a style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.65rem 2.25rem; background: #F59E0B; color: #fff; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.03em;" href="/categories">ดูสินค้าทั้งหมด</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>', '<div style="font-family: \'Sarabun\',sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; color: #374151; line-height: 1.9;">\n\n<span style="display: inline-block; background: #FFF7ED; color: #f59e0b; border: 1px solid #FDE68A; border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">OEM Guide</span>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">What Is OEM Mascara Packaging?</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">Key components of OEM mascara packaging:</p>\n\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0 0 2rem; padding: 0;">\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Tube — PP, ABS, or Aluminum body</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Wand &amp; Brush — various sizes, shapes, and bristle types</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Wiper Ring — controls formula pickup per application</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>Label &amp; Decoration — Sleeve, Hot Stamp, or Direct Print</li>\n</ul>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Mascara Wand Types and Their Results</h2>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Choosing the Right Mascara Tube for Your OEM Brand Positioning</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">Mascara packaging must communicate brand positioning at first glance. Key considerations:</p>\n\n<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Tube shape: cylindrical, flat, or elongated slim</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Material: PP (budget) vs ABS (premium) vs Aluminum (luxury)</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Color &amp; Finish: Black Matte, Glossy, Rose Gold, Holographic</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Fill volume: 7ml–15ml depending on distribution channel</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: fle