id #FDE68A;border-radius:999px;padding:0.2rem 0.75rem;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">OEM Guide</span><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Why 2025 Packaging Trends Matter for Thai OEM Brands</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">5 mega-trends shaping OEM packaging for Thai brands in 2025:</p><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Trend 1 — Sustainable & Eco Packaging</h2><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Trend 2 — Minimalist & Clean Design</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">Modern consumers are fatigued by cluttered, over-designed packaging. Clean Design focuses on:</p><ul style="list-style:none;margin:0 0 2rem;padding:0;"><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Large typography on white or neutral backgrounds</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Reducing SKU clutter to essential information only</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Color block in Earth tones: Warm Sand, Clay, Sage Green</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>Simple but meaningful unboxing experience</span></li><li style="padding:0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0;color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;line-height:1.75;"><span style="color:#F59E0B;font-size:1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">▸</span><span>No Excess Packaging — eliminating unnecessary packaging layers</span></li></ul><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Trend 3 — Airless & Protective Technology</h2><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Trend 4 — Premiumization on a Budget</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">Mid-tier brands are trading up their image without raising prices by using these techniques:</p><u