ont-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>How to Apply Packaging Trends Without Increasing Costs</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">No need to implement all trends at once. Choose 1–2 that best match your Brand DNA:</p><div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0.6rem;margin-bottom:2rem;"><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.55rem 0.75rem;background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:8px;"><span style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span><span style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">Start with Soft Touch Coating — highest ROI, lowest cost</span></div><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.55rem 0.75rem;background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:8px;"><span style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span><span style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">Add QR Code linking to a Landing Page — near-zero cost</span></div><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.55rem 0.75rem;background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:8px;"><span style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span><span style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">Switch to Stock Eco Bag instead of plastic bags — comparable cost</span></div><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.55rem 0.75rem;background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:8px;"><span style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span><span style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">Use Minimalist Label Design — reduces print cost and looks more premium</span></div></div><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>FAQ — Packaging Trends 2025</h2><div style="border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;margin:2.25rem 0;"></div><h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:2.75rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.65rem;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:6px;height:1.3em;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></span>Conclusion</h2><p style="margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:#475569;font-size:0.94rem;line-height:1.85;">2025 Packaging Trends are clearly converging on three directions: Sustainability, low-cost Premiumization, and Digital Integration. Thai OEM brands that anticipate these shifts and invest wisely will gain a significant competitive advantage.</p><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b 0%,#0f172a 100%);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem 1.75rem;text-align:center;margin-top:2.5rem;"><p style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Consult a packaging trend expert for your brand.</p><a href="/categories" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:1rem;padding:0.65rem 2.25rem;background:#F59E0B;color:#fff;border-radius:999px;font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:800;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.03em;">Browse All Products</a></div></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
